== Bundt Cakes ==

Keep @Butter Toffee Bundt Cakes{4} and @Chocolate Caramel Lava Cakes{4} frozen or
refrigerated until ready to eat; best if used within 3 days. If frozen, thaw in
the refrigerator (at 40 degrees) overnight or at room temperature for
~{2-3%hours} before eating.

RECOMMENDED: Remove plastic wrap from #trays{}; microwave until warmed through,
~{50-60%seconds} for Butter Toffee Bundt Cakes or ~{35-45%seconds} for Filled
Chocolate Bundt Cakes. (Do not overheat.) Let cakes cool ~{1-2%minutes}, then
turn out onto #plates{} and serve.

OVEN ALTERNATIVE: Preheat #oven{} to 350 degrees. Remove plastic wrap from trays;
place on a #baking sheet{} and bake until warmed through,
~{14-16%minutes} for Butter Toffee Bundt Cakes or ~{15-17%minutes} for Filled
Chocolate Bundt Cakes. (Note: Oven times may vary.) Let cakes cool
~{1-2%minutes}, then turn out onto plates and serve.

> These frozen treats are perfect for a cozy winter brunch, on your holiday
> dessert table, or for enjoying around the fire with a cup of cocoa.

== Macarons & Peppermint Almonds ==

Enjoy @French Macarons{12%piece} in six different, delicate flavors and
@SkinnyDipped Dark Chocolate Peppermint Almonds{3.5%ounce} for a sweet,
minty treat.